text: is the 8th single by Mika Nakashima. It peaked on the Oricon weekly charts at #4 and sold roughly 38,429 copies. == Outline== Nakashima covered Original Love's fifth single released in 1993. This single was limited the production to 50,000 copies. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2003 singles Category:Mika Nakashima songs
